## 🚀 Featured Project

### 🌐 AWS S3 Portfolio Website with CloudFront
I deployed my personal portfolio website using AWS cloud services and secured it with a CDN for better performance and HTTPS access.

🔧 **Services Used:**
- Amazon S3 (Static Website Hosting)
- Amazon CloudFront (Content Delivery Network)

⚙️ **What I Implemented:**
- Hosted static website on S3
- Configured public access and permissions
- Integrated CloudFront for fast global delivery
- Enabled HTTPS for secure browsing

